  <h3>Installation and Setup</h3>

  <p><strong>DIY Installation:</strong> Smart controllers are designed for easy installation. If you're comfortable with basic wiring, you can install many systems yourself by replacing your existing timer.</p>

  <p><strong>Professional Installation:</strong> We recommend professional installation because we can:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Optimize your irrigation zones before installing the controller</li>
    <li>Ensure proper watering schedule calibration for your Tampa property</li>
